description: A friend on mine is still looking for 5 more employees for his warehouse. They should be fit, young and motivated. And if they would look good it would be a bonus as my friend is gay as well. Today’s applicant looked just great. Blond, blue-grey eyes and a fantastic smile. But he looked also not really muscular for that kind of job. Before he worked at the post-office and at a restaurant. Obviously he had some problems there but he didn't want to talk about that. And though his salaries before have been quite shitty he now was quite demanding. He was expecting something like 26 000 per month as a friend of him also works in a warehouse and he gets well paid especially the night-shifts. So I was wondering what he would be willing to do in exchange for such a job.
title: Dirty Scout 03
